><div id="w-node-_1bc51462-ca96-cb8c-6429-b492818a3e6a-9ffd7ffe" class="service-hero-title-wrap"><h1 class="service-hero-title">Expert cleaning solutions</h1><p class="service-hero-description">We pride ourselves on delivering top-tier cleaning services designed to meet your unique needs. Our team of skilled professionals utilizes cutting-edge techniques.</p></div><div class="service-hero-image-wrap"><img width="495" loading="eager" alt="Service Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/67591346b4d718be00989131_service-image.avif" class="service-hero-image"/></div></div></div></section><section class="service-one-section section-spacing"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e3a" style="opacity:0" class="w-layout-grid grid-service-one"><a href="/service-static" data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e3b" class="service-one-item w-inline-block"><div><div class="service-one-image-wrap"><img data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e3e" loading="eager" alt="Service Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757cfffc7e5ff9daae7bf57_service-image-01.avif" class="service-one-image"/></div><div class="service-one-info"><h2 data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e40" class="service-one-title">Office cleaning</h2><p class="service-one-description">Designed to maintain a pristine &amp; productive workspace, tailored to your business needs.</p><div class="button-link">Read more</div></div></div></a><a href="/service-static" data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e47" class="service-one-item w-inline-block"><div><div class="service-one-image-wrap"><img data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e4a" loading="eager" alt="Service Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757cfffc7e5ff9daae7bf4b_service-image-02.avif" class="service-one-image"/></div><div class="service-one-info"><div><h3 data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e4d" class="service-one-title">Window cleaning</h3><p class="service-one-description">Crystal-clear window cleaning services that brighten your view of your property.</p><div class="button-link">Read more</div></div></div></div></a><a href="/service-static" data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e54" class="service-one-item w-inline-block"><div><div class="service-one-image-wrap"><img data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e57" loading="eager" alt="Service Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757cfffc7e5ff9daae7bf4f_service-image-03.avif" class="service-one-image"/></div><div class="service-one-info"><h4 data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e59" class="service-one-title">Carpet cleaning</h4><p class="service-one-description">Removes dirt, stains, and allergens, leaving your carpets fresh and revitalized.</p><div class="button-link">Read more</div></div></div></a><a href="/service-static" data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e60" class="service-one-item w-inline-block"><div><div class="service-one-image-wrap"><img data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e63" loading="eager" alt="Service Image" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757cfffc7e5ff9daae7bf53_service-image-04.avif" class="service-one-image"/></div><div class="service-one-info"><h5 data-w-id="b097b7aa-7947-9607-2923-b739e6ac1e65" class="service-one-title">Bedroom cleaning</h5><p class="service-one-description">Ensures a tidy, dust-free, and relaxing environment for your rest.</p><div class="button-link">Read more</div></div></div></a></div></div></section><section class="about-center-section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div class="about-center-wrap"><h2 data-w-id="f2299195-5f0c-7b8e-b8c6-30ac5bdda500" style="opacity:0" class="about-center-title">Delivering superior cleaning services with unwavering dedication</h2><div class="w-layout-grid grid-counter"><div data-w-id="f2299195-5f0c-7b8e-b8c6-30ac5bdda503" style="opacity:0" class="counter-item"><h3 class="counter-number">300<span class="text-primary-2">+</span></h3><h4 class="counter-title">Projects completed</h4></div><div data-w-id="f2299195-5f0c-7b8e-b8c6-30ac5bdda50a" style="opacity:0" class="counter-item"><h3 class="counter-number">98<span class="text-primary-2">%</span></h3><h4 class="counter-title">Client retention rate</h4></div><div data-w-id="f2299195-5f0c-7b8e-b8c6-30ac5bdda511" style="opacity:0" class="counter-item"><h3 class="counter-number">50<span class="text-primary-2">+</span></h3><h4 class="counter-title">Professional cleaners</h4></div></div></div></div></section><section class="pricing-section section-spacing"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div data-w-id="695dd59c-5b4d-cc29-1e73-574dfd33b153" style="opacity:0" class="section-title text-center"><h2>Our pricing</h2></div><div class="w-layout-grid grid-pricing"><div data-w-id="695dd59c-5b4d-cc29-1e73-574dfd33b157" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-gray-3"><div><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price">$19</h2><div>/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title">Basic cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description">Ideal for regular maintenance of your home or office.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Dusting</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Vacuuming</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Sweeping and mopping</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Surface cleaning</div></div></div></div></div><div class="pricing-button-wrap"><a href="/pricing" class="button-primary-1 w-button">Get Started</a></div></div><div data-w-id="695dd59c-5b4d-cc29-1e73-574dfd33b179" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-primary-1"><div><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price text-white">$59</h2><div class="text-white">/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title text-white">Standard cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description text-white">Includes all services in the Basic package plus additional services.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title text-white">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c723020_check-icon-02.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div class="text-white">Everything in basic cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c723020_check-icon-02.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div class="text-white">Bathroom scrubbing</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c723020_check-icon-02.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div class="text-white">Kitchen appliance cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c723020_check-icon-02.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div class="text-white">Baseboard and trim cleaning</div></div></div></div></div><div class="pricing-button-wrap"><a href="/pricing" class="button-primary-2 w-button">Get Started</a></div></div><div data-w-id="695dd59c-5b4d-cc29-1e73-574dfd33b19b" style="opacity:0" class="pricing-item bg-gray-3"><div><div class="pricing-wrap"><h2 class="pricing-price">$119</h2><div>/ visit</div></div><h3 class="pricing-title">Deep cleaning package</h3><p class="pricing-description">Perfect for seasonal cleaning or move-ins/outs.</p><div class="pricing-list-wrap"><h4 class="pricing-list-title">Includes:</h4><div class="pricing-list"><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Everything in standard cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Carpet cleaning</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>Window washing</div></div><div class="pricing-list-item"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d2082d3074878c72301f_check-icon-01.svg" alt="Check Icon" class="pricing-icon"/><div>High dusting (e.g., ceiling fans)</div></div></div></div></div><div class="pricing-button-wrap"><a href="/pricing" class="button-primary-1 w-button">Get Started</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="request-demo-section"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container"><div data-w-id="4238f0ff-1566-f521-9f15-c855e1dafc9e" style="opacity:0" class="w-layout-grid grid-request-form"><div class="request-demo-image-wrap"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6757d9461e0346b02f5d4fd2_contact-image.avif" alt="Contact Image" class="request-demo-image"/></div><div class="request-demo-form-wrap"><h4 class="request-demo-title">Request a service</h4><div class="no-margin w-form"><form id="wf-form-Request-A-Demo-Form" name="wf-form-Request-A-Demo-Form" data-name="Request A Demo Form" method="get" data-wf-page-id="6757cb7ca93fe3139ffd7ffe" data-wf-element-id="4238f0ff-1566-f521-9f15-c855e1dafca5"><label for="Name">Name</label><input class="form-input contact-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="Name" data-name="Name" placeholder="Dennis barrett" type="text" id="Name"/><label for="Email">Email</label><input class="form-input contact-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="Email" data-name="Email" placeholder="example@gmail.com" type="email" id="Email" required=""/><div class="form-input-wrap"><div class="input-group no-margin"><label for="Phone">Phone</label><input class="form-input contact-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="Phone" data-name="Phone" placeholder="+1234567890" type="tel" id="Phone"/></div><div class="input-group no-margin"><label for="Field">Select service</label><select id="Field" name="Field" data-name="Field" class="form-select contact-input w-select"><option value="Another option">Select service</option><option value="">Office cleaning</option><option value="First">Window cleaning</option><option value="Second">Carpet cleaning</option><option value="Third">Bedroom cleaning</option></select></div></div><div class="form-input-wrap"><div class="input-group no-margin"><label for="Location">Location</label><input class="form-input contact-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="Location" data-name="Location" placeholder="Los angeles" type="text" id="Location"/></div><div class="input-group no-margin"><label for="Date">Date</label><input class="form-input contact-input w-input" maxlength="256" name="Date" data-name="Date" placeholder="dd-mm-yy" type="text" id="Date"/></div></div><div class="hero-form-button-wrap"><input type="submit" data-wait="Please wait..." class="button-primary-2 button-full w-button" value="Book an appointment"/></div></form><div class="success-message w-form-done"><div>Thank you! Your submission has been received!</div></div><div class="error-message w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div><div class="request-demo-detail"><div>OR</div><div class="request-demo-wrap"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6762529184f5394d604f57de_call-icon-dark.svg" alt="" class="contact-icons"/><h5 class="request-a-demo-title">Call us on <a href="tel:+1(234)567-8901" class="request-demo-link">+1 (234) 567-8901</a> </h5></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c4650" style="opacity:0" class="faq-section section-spacing"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-medium w-container"><div class="section-title text-center"><h2>Frequently asked questions</h2></div><div class="faq-wrap last"><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c4657" class="accordion-heading"><h3 class="accordion-title">What services do you offer?</h3><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(-90deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We offer a comprehensive range of cleaning services, including residential cleaning, commercial janitorial services, carpet cleaning, window washing, and deep cleaning. Our services are tailored to meet the unique needs of each client.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c4664" class="accordion-heading"><h4 class="accordion-title">How do I book a cleaning service?</h4><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">Booking a service is easy! You can schedule an appointment online through our website, give us a call, or send us an email. Our customer service team is ready to assist you with your booking.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c4671" class="accordion-heading"><h5 class="accordion-title">What is your cancellation policy?</h5><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We understand that plans can change. If you need to cancel or reschedule your appointment, please contact us at least 24 hours in advance. Cancellations made less than 24 hours before the scheduled service may incur a fee.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item"><div data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c467e" class="accordion-heading"><h6 class="accordion-title">Can I request the same cleaning team for each visit?</h6><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">We strive to provide consistency for our clients. If you prefer the same cleaning team for each visit, please let us know, and we will do our best to accommodate your request.</p></div></div><div class="accordion-item last"><div data-w-id="f9602116-2dc7-f08a-5203-6e44d61c468b" class="accordion-heading"><h6 class="accordion-title">Do I need to be home during the cleaning?</h6><div class="accordion-icon-wrap open"><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="horizontal-icon"></div><div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0, 0)" class="vertical-icon"></div></div></div><div style="height:0px" class="accordion-content-wrapper"><p class="accordion-content">It’s up to you! You can choose to be present during the cleaning, or you can provide us with access to your home or office. Our trusted staff will ensure your property is secure and well-cared for.</p></div></div></div></div></section><footer class="footer"><div class="container w-container"><div data-w-id="d7558fd6-59ae-df5d-4e33-ad7117a64f1d" class="w-layout-grid grid-footer"><h4 class="no-margin">Claim your free first Cleaning today.</h4><div id="w-node-d7558fd6-59ae-df5d-4e33-ad7117a64f20-17a64f1b" class="button-inline"><a href="/contact" data-w-id="ee9ec817-088f-cbd3-ff7f-9b8b0cb30061" class="button-primary-1-icon w-inline-block"><div>Claim free visit</div><div class="button-primary-icon-wrap"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6756c558622788afc19a5f32_arrow-icon.svg" alt="Arrow Icon" class="button-icon"/><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6756c558622788afc19a5f32_arrow-icon.svg" alt="Arrow Icon" class="button-hover-icon"/></div></a><a href="tel:+1-394-495-5993" class="button-primary-1 w-button">Call us: +1-394-495-5993</a></div></div><div class="w-layout-grid grid-footer-item"><div id="w-node-d7558fd6-59ae-df5d-4e33-ad7117a64f26-17a64f1b" data-w-id="d7558fd6-59ae-df5d-4e33-ad7117a64f26" class="footer-item"><a href="/" aria-label="link" class="brand w-inline-block"><img loading="eager" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6756b988bb35f025028d3f34/6764eb2948154505535d87ea_cleaninger.svg" alt="" class="footer-logo"/></a><p class="footer-description">We handle repairs &amp; maintenance for all appliances with expertise &amp; efficiency to ensure your appliances.</p></div><div class="w-layout-grid grid-footer-items"><div data-w-id="d7558fd6-59ae-df5d-4e33-ad7117a64f2c" class="footer-links"><a href="/" class="footer-link">Home</a><a href="/home-2" class="footer-link">Home 2</a><a href="/about" class="footer-link">About</a><a href="/services" aria-current="page" class="footer-link w--current">Services</a><a href="/service-static" class="footer-link">Servi